Uses of Package
org.codehaus.staxmate

  • Packages that use org.codehaus.staxmate 
    Package Description
    org.codehaus.staxmate
    Package contains factories for constructing input and output processing components (such as input cursors).
  • Classes in org.codehaus.staxmate used by org.codehaus.staxmate 
    Class and Description
    SMInputFactory
    Factory class used to create SMInputCursor instances.
    SMOutputFactory
    Factory class used to create root-level outputter object (like SMOutputDocument and SMRootFragment) instances, which are roots (global for documents, or local for fragments) of output content.
